            "High-Quality Export",
            "Undo/Redo Support",
            "Offline First",
            "JSON Editor"
        ],
        "primary_use_case": "Generating professional app store screenshots with customizable templates and device mockups.",
        "open_issues": 0,
        "cover_image_prompt": "A digital artist's workbench, bathed in soft, creative light. In the center, a sleek, modern smartphone is held by a pair of hands, displaying a vibrant app interface. Surrounding the phone are floating elements: a stylized 'Play Store' icon, an 'App Store' icon, and various professional-looking frames and templates. Digital particles representing design elements like text blocks and device borders flow from a glowing 'Snapframe' logo towards the phone, seamlessly integrating to create a polished, marketing-ready app screenshot. The overall style is a clean, 3D isometric illustration with a focus on clarity and a modern aesthetic."
